{"type": "article", "id": 16473, "title": "杂技灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-23T06:40:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000343dirKkjMsaHupR8Zz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏灯的灯罩和灯座是分开的，仅依靠磁铁吸引。因而长条形的灯罩可以转动成不同的角度，与桌面倾斜或者与之保持水平。法国设计师 Marc Venot 和设计品牌商 Normann Copenhagen 共同推出了这款灯，设计者将它命名为 Acrobat（杂技），缘于杂技演员可以转动到不同角度而不会失去平衡。一共有黑、白、灰、深紫四种颜色。售价 410 美元，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/acrobat?v=502122\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143723nW32fwyLVrQmHxs0.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"449\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143723JdjVPOgIEvk2Nm0R.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"728\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143724418KHBS6fFuaNigh.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"301\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.31354167\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143724FGEqCd3NeoOinhV8.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"427\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}